::Shadow Wing::
She swooped down and found Ramulus in stasis lock.
"Oh No."
She tried to lift him up in her beast mode.  She strainded but her was to 
heavy for her to lift.
"Shadow Wing Maximize!"
She transformed and tried to pick him up again. He was still to heavy for 
her.  She dragged him to the Arc.  She left him long enough to locate a CR 
chamber that was undamaged in the blast.  She dragged him to the CR chamber 
and tried to put him into it.
"After this, your going on a diet."
She finally got him inside the chamber and switched it on.

She sat back and took a breather.  She needed it.  She then realized that 
other bots needed her help outside and went back out to try to do what she 
could.
